name: BIBI2.0
description: BIBI2.0 is an upgraded version of BIBI. Strengthen ecological integration to make BIBI more perfect. At the same time, it is a completely community driven and autonomous new Web3 ecosystem, focusing on the dissemination of MEME culture and the construction of Web3 communities, aiming to establish a creative, interactive, and inclusive learning community. All community members will benefit from participating in organized activities and promotion. MISSION BIBI2.0 will build an educative, interactive, and inclusive community, an ecosystem where community members will benefit from their participation in organized events and promotion. VISION BIBI2.0 aims to accelerate its growth and become the most transformative leadership community.We will enrich the lives of the community so that it will benefit the BIBI2.0 ecosystem.
